{"tid":2416261,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【恥笑】有文宣page本來就執笠畀文匯報起死回生","createTime":"2021-02-21T01:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T00:51:42.000Z","uid":42375,"like":198,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"ca34b9291366c05a0c174ee9bd1430a76f1b063f","tid":2416261,"uid":42375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T01:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7zH4gEm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zH4gEm.jpg&h=590255b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzy7eq2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftzy7eq2.jpg&h=899a3b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PS64053.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPS64053.jpg&h=a245dcbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【《自由港》編輯部衷心感激港獨媒體《文匯報》大力宣傳】<br />\n<br />\n今日《文滙報》以頗大篇幅報道本刊，令文刊讀者在短時間之內有可觀的上升，因此編輯團隊特意撰文對《文匯報》的宣傳聊表感謝之情。<br />\n<br />\n正如二月號當中所講，編輯團隊曾經不止一次起過停刊念頭，文匯報今次大力宣傳，可說是變相延續我們這本「港獨刊物」的壽命，編輯團隊感激不盡，愛你唷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被文匯報大力推廣的2021年2月號全文：<br />\nISSUU:<br />\n<a href=\"https://issuu.com/harbouroffreedom/docs/01_cn___b38278628b88d2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fissuu.com%2Fharbouroffreedom%2Fdocs%2F01_cn___b38278628b88d2&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=3a19c3a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://issuu.com/harbouroffreedom/docs/01_cn___b38278628b88d2</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle Drive:<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/16pUtC5O8dTHD9gXIlZCrxggo-i_j-RHA/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F16pUtC5O8dTHD9gXIlZCrxggo-i_j-RHA%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=a12743ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/16pUtC5O8dTHD9gXIlZCrxggo-i_j-RHA/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n如果可以麻煩大家follow埋我哋其他嘅社交媒體，了解最新消息：<br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<